t: "We have made sacrificial camels ňĻand cattleňļ among the symbols of God, in which there is ňĻmuchňļ good for you. So pronounce the Name of God over them when they are lined up ňĻfor sacrificeňļ. Once they have fallen ňĻlifelessňļ on their sides, you may eat from their meat, and feed the needy‚ÄĒthose who do not beg, and those who do. In this way We have subjected these ňĻanimalsňļ to you so that you may be grateful"